<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
      <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/Imagens/favicon.ico">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/CSS/theme.css">
    <title>Convidar Testers - Ally</title>
</head>


<body>

    {{> _skip_links}}
    <div id="dashboard">

        <!-- header -->
        <header class="headerDashboard">
            <button class="menutoggle" aria-expanded="false">Menu</button>
            <h1>Convidar Testers</h1>
            <div class="utilities">
                <span class="user">Olá {{nome}}!</span>
                <a tabindex="0" class="logout" href="/users/logout">Sair</a>
            </div>
        </header>
        <!-- /header -->
        {{> _sidebar}}

        <main id="conteudo">
            <!-- breadcrumbs -->
            <nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
                <ol class="breadcrumb">
                    <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/">Testes </a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="breadcrumb-item active" aria-current="page">Convidar Tester</li>
                </ol>
            </nav>
            <!-- / breadcrumbs -->
            <!-- tela de aguarde -->
            <section class="main-panel">
                <div class="panel-info">
                    <h2>Pronto! Agora é só esperar...</h2><br>
                    <p>Quando seus convidados aceitarem seu convite,<br> você
                        receberá uma notificação no seu e-mail e por aqui. </p>
                    <a class="btn-orientacoes" href="/">Voltar para todos os testes</a>
                </div>
            </section>
            <!-- / tela de aguarde -->
        </main>
    </div>
    <!-- footer -->
    <footer id="rodape" class="footerDashboard">
        <p><span class="footer__copyright">&copy;</span> Ally 2020</p>
        <a href="/contato">Entre em contato</a>
    </footer>
    <!-- / footer -->

    </div>

    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.1/js/all.min.js">
    </script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-2.2.4.min.js"
        integrity="sha256-BbhdlvQf/xTY9gja0Dq3HiwQF8LaCRTXxZKRutelT44=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="/Javascript/mobileDashboard.js"></script>